my understanding:
fill 3Ljug full, pour 3Ljug into 5Ljug, fill 3Ljug full, pour 3Ljug into 5Ljug until it is full. (Now there is 1L IN 3L jug)
empty 5ljug pour 3Ljug into 5Ljug (there is 1L in 5L jug). fill 3ljug until full, pour 3Ljug into 5ljug (1L +3L= 4L)

